#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "Kevlar-lined small quadruped peto"
msgid_plural "Kevlar-lined small quadruped petos"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kevlar-lined small quadruped peto'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A heavy mattress-like armor of cloth, leather and thick linings of Kevlar, "
"originally used as protection in bullfighting. Nowadays usually worn by "
"canines in the service of local law enforcement, that protects from "
"shoulders to abdomen.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped "
"including a dog."
msgstr ""

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
